Title: Primary Genomic Annotations (hg38)
Description: Primary Human genomic annotations curated for use with RLSuite.

Title: Primary Genomic Annotations (mm10)
Description: Primary Mouse genomic annotations curated for use with RLSuite.

Title: Full Genomic Annotations (hg38)
Description: Full Human genomic annotations curated for use with RLSuite.

Title: Full Genomic Annotations (mm10)
Description: Full Mouse genomic annotations curated for use with RLSuite.

Title: R-loop Binding Proteins
Description: R-loop-binding proteins discovered from mass-spec studies.

Title: Gene Expression
Description: Gene expression count tables from matched RNA-Seq experiments corresponding to R-loop profiling. The counts, TPM, and VST-transformed counts are provided.

Title: Feature Enrichment per Sample
Description: Genomic feature enrichment stats for each peakset in RLBase.

Title: Feature Enrichment per RL-Region
Description: Genomic feature enrichment stats for the RL-Regions in RLBase.

Title: GS-Signal
Description: Bin-level read counts for RLBase samples around R-loop sites discovered using long-read SMRF-Seq (gold-standard sites).

Title: FFT-Model
Description: Stacked classifier for deciding whether samples successfully mapped R-loops.

Title: Feature-Prep Model
Description: Model for transforming dataset features prior to classification.

Title: RLFS-Test Results
Description: The results from RLFS (R-loop-forming sequences) analysis on all RLBase samples via the RLSeq package.

Title: RLRegion Annotations
Description: R-loop regions (rlregions) derived from S9.6-based and dRNH-based samples ('All' group), annotated with genomic features.

Title: RLRegion Metadata
Description: R-loop regions (rlregions) derived from S9.6-based and dRNH-based samples ('All' group), with descriptive metadata.

Title: RLRegion Read Counts
Description: Read count tables from RLBase samples quantified across the R-loop regions (rlregions) derived from both S9.6-based and dRNH-based samples ('All' group).

Title: RLBase Sample Manifest
Description: The hand-curated manifest of all RLBase samples with descriptive metadata and some sample-level analysis results.
